  "text": "The organization of the manuscript is as follows. In Sections 2 and 3, we recall some preliminary definitions and results about topological entropy and Hubbard trees that will be used below. In Section 4, we give a detailed description of the weak critical markings of postcritically-finite polynomials and their induced partitions in the dynamical plane. We then introduce Thurston's entropy algorithm in Section 5, and prove the main theorem (Theorem 1.2) in Section 6. Proposition 2. [CITATION_1] . Assume that π is a surjective semi-conjugacy",
